<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard | Momentum Fit</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-layout">
    <%- include('../partials/sidebar.ejs') %>

    <main class="app-content">
        <%- include('../partials/app-header.ejs', { title: 'Vis√£o Geral' }) %>

        <div class="dashboard-wrapper">
            
            <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: white; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                    Ol√°, <%= user.name.split(' ')[0] %>! Ì±ã
                </h1>
                <p style="color: #888;">Preparado para superar seus limites hoje?</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stats-row">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-data">
                        <h3><%= stats.workoutsCompleted || 0 %></h3>
                        <p>Treinos no M√™s</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon-wrapper" style="color: #ff9f43; background: rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.1);">
                        <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-data">
                        <h3><%= stats.streak || 0 %></h3>
                        <p>Dias de Foco</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon-wrapper" style="color: #00cec9; background: rgba(0, 206, 201, 0.1);">
                        <i class="fas fa-weight"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-data">
                        <h3><%= stats.currentWeight || '--' %> <span style="font-size: 1rem; color: #666;">kg</span></h3>
                        <p>Peso Atual</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                
                <div>
                    <div class="content-card next-workout-card">
                        <div class="card-header-flex">
                            <h3 class="card-title">
                                <i class="fas fa-calendar-day" style="color: var(--primary-color);"></i>
                                Pr√≥ximo Treino
                            </h3>
                            <span style="background: #222; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #aaa;">
                                <%= nextWorkout ? nextWorkout.category : 'Geral' %>
                            </span>
                        </div>

                        <% if (nextWorkout) { %>
                            <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: white; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                <%= nextWorkout.title %>
                            </h2>
                            <p style="color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px;"><%= nextWorkout.description || 'Foco na execu√ß√£o e controle de carga.' %></p>

                            <div class="workout-detail-row">
                                <div class="w-detail"><i class="far fa-clock"></i> <%= nextWorkout.duration || 60 %> min</div>
                                <div class="w-detail"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> <%= nextWorkout.exerciseCount || 0 %> Exerc√≠cios</div>
                                <div class="w-detail"><i class="fas fa-signal"></i> <%= nextWorkout.intensity || 'M√©dia' %></div>
                            </div>

                            <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px;">
                                <a href="/workouts/start/<%= nextWorkout.id %>" class="btn btn-primary" style="flex: 1;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Iniciar Agora
                                </a>
                                <a href="/workouts/details/<%= nextWorkout.id %>" class="btn btn-outline">
                                    Ver Detalhes
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 0;">
                                <div style="color: #333; font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></div>
                                <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 10px;">Tudo feito por hoje!</h3>
                                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Voc√™ n√£o tem treinos agendados para agora.</p>
                                <a href="/client/workouts" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Ver Biblioteca</a>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-card" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                        <div class="card-header-flex">
                            <h3 class="card-title">Seu Progresso</h3>
                            <select style="background: #000; border: 1px solid #333; color: white; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 6px;">
                                <option>√öltimos 30 dias</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div style="height: 200px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #444; border: 1px dashed #333;">
                            <p>Gr√°fico de evolu√ß√£o de carga ser√° exibido aqui.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="content-card" style="margin-bottom: 30px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(190, 242, 2, 0.05) 0%, #111 100%); border-color: rgba(190, 242, 2, 0.2);">
                        <div class="card-header-flex">
                            <h3 class="card-title" style="color: var(--primary-color);">
                                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Coach IA
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <p style="color: #ddd; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                            "Notei que voc√™ manteve a const√¢ncia essa semana. Para o treino de hoje, tente aumentar a carga no Leg Press em 5% se sentir seguran√ßa."
                        </p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: right;">
                            <a href="/client/ai-coach" style="color: var(--primary-color); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;">Abrir Chat <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-card">
                        <h3 class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Acesso R√°pido</h3>
                        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;">
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="justify-content: flex-start; border-color: #333;">
                                <i class="fas fa-camera" style="width: 25px;"></i> Registrar Foto
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="justify-content: flex-start; border-color: #333;">
                                <i class="fas fa-weight-scale" style="width: 25px;"></i> Atualizar Peso
                            </a>
                            <a href="/client/ai-coach" class="btn btn-outline" style="justify-content: flex-start; border-color: #333;">
                                <i class="fas fa-question-circle" style="width: 25px;"></i> D√∫vida R√°pida
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

</body>
</html>
